c: 47
v: 20
t: "And those who beieve say \"Would that divine revelation [as desired by us] is sent down!\" But now that an unambiguous revelation about war has been sent down, you [Muhammad] can see those, in whose hearts is a disease, looking at you with the look of one who is about to faint for fear of death! Far better for them woud be [continued to next Verse]"